Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:16.58,Default,Doc,0,0,0,,It's the same as Nagisa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:22.51,Default,Doc,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I cannot tell the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:27.18,Default,Doc,0,0,0,,But I would guess that the same suffering Nagisa-san went through will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.05,0:00:30.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Just a second ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,...she was running around.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.73,0:00:42.03,Default,Doc,0,0,0,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:00:57.96,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Tomoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.79,0:01:01.92,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Who's her father?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:04.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:07.22,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Then you have to keep your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:50.61,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:52.52,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Are you cold at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:56.49,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,As a doll, I don't feel cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:03:00.66,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,But I'm sure her hand is cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:04.79,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,Although I can't even tell that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:10.33,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,The world will soon turn completely white.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.84,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,We need to hurry a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:18.67,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(957.273,415.8)}Episode 21
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:18.67,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(960,712.5)}End of the World
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:29.85,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,The sports day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:30.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:35.11,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,You're not going to run, Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:38.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll be with you the whole day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.45,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Akki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:46.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He might run. If two anchors skipped,\Nthey'd have trouble finding two replacements.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:52.42,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Daddy. Beat Akki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:55.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I said I'll be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.38,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:00.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So you're on my side, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:01.88,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm on your side, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.02,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:13.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:14.77,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:18.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I won't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:19.03,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,One week...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:26.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Two weeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:31.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then a month went by,\Nand Ushio's fever did not go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:36.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She couldn't go to kindergarten, much less leave the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:44.43,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,I don't want you leaving us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:47.68,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,But, looks like there are a variety of issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.57,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,That was a big decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:03.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sanae-san and the old man tried to stop me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:06.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,but I want to be with Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:08.83,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Do you have anything saved up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:09.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Some.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:12.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was saving up for her education.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:13.41,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:16.08,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Good work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:19.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thank you for your guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:28.47,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Take it. Don't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:33.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:37.65,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Of course not. How will I work without it from tomorrow on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:38.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:43.15,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Lend me yours instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.49,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,I'll give it back to you when you return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:49.12,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Come back when Ushio-chan recovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:51.58,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,I'll borrow yours until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.98,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,I'll take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:23.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio stayed home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:26.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We thought about putting her in a hospital but decided not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:31.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Since we don't know the treatment for it,\Nthere was no point in staying at a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:36.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Most of all, Ushio wanted to stay home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:39.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's change into new pajamas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:39.96,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:45.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You don't have to get up. I'll change you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.68,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I can do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:03.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's all right if you can't do it yourself right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:05.40,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio can't get changed alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She can't go to the bathroom alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She can only eat soft foods.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.29,0:07:19.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Won't those peaceful days ever come back again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:30.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio, do you have anything you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:33.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you do, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:36.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll buy you anything; toys or snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.31,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I want to go on a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:44.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:46.48,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I want to go on a trip with Daddy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:50.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That wasn't fun at all, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:52.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was in such a bad mood and yelled the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:55.58,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.87,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I want to go on another trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:02.08,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,On a train with Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:04.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Once you get better, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:08.46,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I want to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:14.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio... Don't ask for the impossible and trouble me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:24.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I can't even grant the one wish my only daughter has? {ep20}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:27.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa... {ep20}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:29.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What should I do? {ep20}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If only you were here at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:38.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm... {ep20}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:43.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,My family might just be getting toyed with by this city. {ep20}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:48.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Given happiness, then having it snatched away. {ep20}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:52.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:56.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I will save Ushio no matter what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I will save Ushio!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Please look after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:05.48,San,San,0,0,0,,Have a good trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:06.90,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:11.57,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:15.03,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:22.71,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Don't be so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:25.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, I don't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:28.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I still have some savings,\Nso we'll be okay for a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.59,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I'll beat you up if you're lying to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:31.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.80,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Then fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:40.35,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,There are things a man has to protect even if it kills his pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:41.52,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:44.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:47.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If I run into something serious, I'll let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:12.34,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:15.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:17.68,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That's wise of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:20.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:27.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,People built this hospital by sacrificing the forest that was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:31.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What will the next sacrifice be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:36.70,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,A hill on the outskirts of town is getting dug up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:39.70,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Apparently, they're building a shopping mall there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:43.70,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It'll be convenient, so it's great for people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:54.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,From the moment you brought the near-death Nagisa here, Nagisa was linked to this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:58.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And Nagisa's daughter, Ushio, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:08.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Does... Is going through change a pain for the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:14.48,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I think it's got nothing to do with pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.86,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,"Oh, I'm changing."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.07,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I think that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:30.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If people's deaths are a part of changing, then do we have to accept that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:35.71,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,People build hospitals because they don't want to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:56.82,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Let this city and its people be blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you thirsty?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you want some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:02.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's cold, so drink slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you go too fast, you'll get a stomachache.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:14.81,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:16.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:17.44,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.32,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I want to go on a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:27.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sure. After you get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:29.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:32.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you want to go to that flower patch again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:35.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ah, but going north now would be cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:36.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's go south.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:41.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,To a place where it's warm, beautiful, and there's clean air.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:42.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Or-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:43.26,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I want to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,After you get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:49.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I've told you so many times, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:51.31,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.23,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I want to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:54.44,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,To the flower patch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:56.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.11,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,It has to be now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:03.07,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I want to go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:16.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:19.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll let you have your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:20.75,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:24.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But you have to let me know when you're not feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:25.84,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:27.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:36.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll give you a piggy back ride. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:39.52,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I'll walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:40.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:45.49,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I want to walk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:46.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:49.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then let's walk together as far as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:50.53,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:52.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:54.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's make this a fun trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:57.50,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Ushio?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:13.56,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:17.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You have to let me know the moment you're not feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We'll go to a doctor then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:20.56,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:45.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:45.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:01.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you like snow, Ushio?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:19.37,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:22.33,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Do you like it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:29.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, I like it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Can you keep walking, Ushio?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you want to rest a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:35.51,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.31,0:16:38.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's get in a car before it starts coming down hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll give you a piggy back ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:41.69,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:34.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:50.42,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:51.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What is it, Ushio?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:54.84,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:57.30,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Are we on the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:01.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. We're on the train already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:05.56,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,It's dark... Is it night?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's right. It's midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:10.69,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:12.82,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.32,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:16.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:20.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I love you, too, Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:34.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:35.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:42.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,USHIO!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:00.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:02.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I don't want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:04.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Save Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:16.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Someone... Someone save Ushio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:20.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:56.84,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:14.23,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,How many more steps will it take to get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:17.94,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,Could we be only a step away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:24.24,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,Or, do we have to walk without end?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:55.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I hate this city. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:21:00.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's full of all the memories I want to forget about. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:10.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,{\fs70.2}Go to school every day, chat with friends, and then go back to the home I don't even want to go back to. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:16.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Will something eventually change, doing this? {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:20.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Will that day come? {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:33.23,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sweet bean bread! {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:37.69,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Do you like this school? {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:43.40,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I really, really love it. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:46.87,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But nothing can stay unchanged. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:55.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If I talk to her here, Nagisa and I\Nwill meet and eventually date.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:22:00.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But, maybe it was better if I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:03.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It might've been better if we'd never met.
